      <title>特朗普威胁后中国承诺接收非法移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/china-promises-to-take-back-illegal-migrants-after-trump-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对哥伦比亚征收高达 50% 的关税，以抗议该国拒绝接收被驱逐的移民。此后，中国承诺接受在美国境内的非法中国公民返回。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/china-promises-to-take-back-illegal-migrants-after-trump-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 07:55:46 GMT</pubDate>
